name: Party at Sunday
description: [SongMoods] Is a serie of experimental digital works by Rodstoulle (Hedonistic Futures) in which the author, heavily influenced by a determined song, try to incorporate it on the visual aspects of his artwork in a process of synesthesia. | "All my friends will get bored / And all my friends are assholes / Every trip is around one now / Every eye is green or brown"  |  [SongMoods #02: SONG: PARTY AT SUNDAY, by Cosmonauts].
